              <p style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--text);">John 3:16 reminds us that <span style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:600;">God's love is unconditional and eternal</span>. For daily life, it means living without fear — you are deeply loved. Let that love flow outward to everyone you meet today. 🌟</p>
            </div>

